      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775237690804,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Without cache, cost grows linearly (re-reading everything each turn).\nWith cache, only new tokens pay full price — the growing prefix is 90% cheaper.\nFor a 50-turn coding session, savings can exceed 85%.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Without cache, cost grows linearly (re-reading everything each turn).\nWith cache, only new tokens pay full price — the growing prefix is 90% cheaper.\nFor a 50-turn coding session, savings can exceed 85%.",
